narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Evan Agnetta is a Dentist, Orthodontics and Dentofacial Orthopedics provider based in Knoxville, TN. From 2021-03 through 2021-12, this provider received $176K in Medicaid payments across 3K claims serving 2K beneficiaries, billing 3 distinct procedure codes.

narrative.title: Key Findings
items: 82% of billing is concentrated in D8670 (D8670), indicating significant specialization in this service.
Billing stopped in 2021-12, suggesting this provider is no longer active in Medicaid. Abrupt cessation of billing can be a risk indicator.
